{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1d78f5de19","title":"在《中国人民政治协商会议共同纲领》起草过程中的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4cfa9cfd76","index":0,"year":1949,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"1d78f5de19"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"cba57b9ade","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东对《中国人民政治协商会议共同纲领》草案作过多次修改，写了一些批语，这些文献资料没有全部保存下来。这里选入的5次批语，只是一个侧面的反映。"},{"id":"1b4de05a40","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"乔木，即胡乔木，当时任毛泽东的秘书。这5次批语都是写给他的。"},{"id":"ec0ad5e0eb","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指经毛泽东1949年9月6日修改的《中国人民政治协商会议共同纲领》草案，修改的底本是纲领草案（1949年9月5日，初稿）铅印件。"},{"id":"879bfd1654","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指周恩来，当时受中共中央委派主持起草《中国人民政治协商会议共同纲领》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f2c012572c","type":"title","text":"在《中国人民政治协商会议共同纲领》起草过程中的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"cba57b9ade","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"1b4de05a40","type":"paragraph","text":"纲领共印三十份，全部交我，希望今晚十点左右交来。题应是《共同纲领》","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"ec0ad5e0eb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"879bfd1654","type":"paragraph","text":"九月三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"163be8be75","type":"paragraph","text":"你应注意睡眠乔木：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"5e142e4791","type":"paragraph","text":"今\"晚付印的纲领，请先送清样给我校对一次，然后付印。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"d31545401a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"1af8e74a4e","type":"subtitle","text":"即三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"775d135359","type":"paragraph","text":"即刻付印，一小时内交我。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"2cfaa0ea37","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"9ba6a49948","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"1bd782424e","type":"paragraph","text":"照此改正，印成小册子一千本。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"dd3bdc89e1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"9a77721eff","type":"paragraph","text":"九月六日","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"8edd84357e","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]指1949年9月3日。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"33ea7c1516","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"f22e83971f","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木：","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"2240431e57","type":"paragraph","text":"即刻印一百份，于下午八时左右送交周副主席”。但不要拆版，侯起草小组修正后，再印1000份。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"59596b6634","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"},{"id":"0422975c9d","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十一日下午四时半","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"1d78f5de19"}],"